				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The 2 attribute bits select which out of the 4 palettes that a tile is using. You don't have 2 bits for every tile though, they are shared on a 2x2 tile basis. So each attribute table byte contains attributes for 4x4 tiles (2x2 + 2x2 + 2x2 + 2x2).</div>

