					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I put stuff up there no matter what. My first attempt at a Final Fantasy style map engine had me putting stuff starting at $2020 and ending before the last row. It was a total disaster. On my NTSC TV, you can just barely see the middle of the top row (I can see the updates on FF1 if I look at the very top of the screen). So I would definitely start at $2000.
<br />
<br />Writing $00 to the screen is good to do at your reset routine, because if someone does a soft reset while playing your game, you'll most likely want to have a clear screen before you do anything to it.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.freewebs.com/the_bott/" class="postlink">-Owner of Poultry Games</a></div>
